{"tid":2510074,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我和鄰居大姐姐的故事（8）","createTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T11:38:04.000Z","uid":189997,"like":239,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d54bca8b78492cc395aebcda216a6cad2e9bbffa","tid":2510074,"uid":189997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"一朝早起身返工就見到爆post係幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家支持，黎到第8個post喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老規矩，爆post今晚會加更<br />\n每100個正評都會再加更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之一路走來，多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4d449a01fa35d4d4ea6932c43a4cba6d6f13d8","tid":2510074,"uid":264734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:18.000Z","msg":"新po加更！"},{"pid":"517a6d6e54d9adaceb9ae679917db2ad0b0920dd","tid":2510074,"uid":396438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:47:42.000Z","msg":"New post Lm"},{"pid":"d2d40e08b41c968ed1903b71372b840293b93b2e","tid":2510074,"uid":120805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"新post留名<br />\n<br />\n威仔記得加更呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69597c4d860355a2f0149dbb80773347d14b8e1b","tid":2510074,"uid":85097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"正評留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d3f9efeea715094e14b26c7499176bc8768285","tid":2510074,"uid":19544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n秋兒姐姐是最好的"},{"pid":"829c5c12a2fa51fec4e6dc764a0d2aa82a58a0f5","tid":2510074,"uid":25619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a805b3fd89c1e6b4c4679826d5beeeea558245c6","tid":2510074,"uid":210807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a35f1322fd4f56ffcbfde9c11f246ca7d328f3","tid":2510074,"uid":97486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4f8be43041d10c5d6c0fa74c04c5aaae003ca7b1","tid":2510074,"uid":210846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"新post留名"},{"pid":"c2957b9cd854c86443e7bb079588ed551bc79a09","tid":2510074,"uid":189997,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"前情提要：秋兒要會考了，會考前夕，阿鋒剖白左當年既感情。其實響秋兒心目中，阿熙又係點既呢? 而熙熙亦都為秋兒姐姐會考作出窩心既打氣&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nPost 1：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229650</a><br />\nPost 2：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2274649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2274649</a><br />\nPost 3：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2300725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2300725</a><br />\nPost 4：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2331531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2331531</a><br />\nPost 5：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2378923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2378923</a><br />\nPost 6：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2441957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2441957</a><br />\nPost 7：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2486247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2486247</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告時間：<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得樓主寫野ok既，又或者想睇下樓主平時會寫埋啲咩戇鳩野既，不妨follow下樓主既IG或者like下facebook page~<br />\n<br />\nig: leafopen3<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/leafopen3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fleafopen3%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=8ec4dd44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/leafopen3/</a><br />\nfb: leafopenleafopen<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leafopenleafopen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleafopenleafopen%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=df7fbfbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leafopenleafopen/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紙言: <a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/authors/37384.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F37384.html&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=182796fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/authors/37384.html</a><br />\n<br />\nPenana: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/52938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F52938&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=181f4b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/52938</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣睇舊故，不妨click入去睇下:<br />\n<br />\n1.《我和一個o camp女女的故事》(愛情/少甜/正傳世界觀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/i/TgG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2FTgG&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=5d2a0d10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/i/TgG</a><br />\n<br />\n2.《我響婚宴酒樓遇到一個教堂妖精，佢話可以幫我回到過去&hellip;》(愛情/少甜/妖精世界觀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/i/UVy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2FUVy&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=2734d0a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/i/UVy</a><br />\n<br />\n3.《我個仔被老屈藏有炸藥》(親情/社會/走甜/正傳世界觀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/i/WQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2FWQU&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=595715bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/i/WQU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/50939/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F50939%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=be683750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/50939/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 《如果蜘蛛俠係香港人&hellip;》(同人/英雄/走甜/Marvel同人世界觀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/i/Ykw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2FYkw&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=1b076a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/i/Ykw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/54279/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F54279%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=42b2da26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/54279/</a><br />\n<br />\n5.《我和鄰居大姐姐的故事》(愛情/少甜/正傳世界觀)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/i/5yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2F5yo&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=da0319cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/i/5yo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/69120/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F69120%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=ce5d2fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/69120/</a>"